                     <li class="divider-vertical"></li>            
                     <li><a href="#" onclick="return false;" rel="tooltip" title="We opened up just the listing feature on Shelflet. Start listing your old/used books!" class="element" data-placement='bottom'><i class="icon-shopping-cart icon-white"></i>Cart<span class="cartItems">0</span></a> 

